INSERT INTO build_errors (
                build_run_id, error_hash, severity, error_code, message,
                file_path, line_number, column_number, suggestion, code_snippet,
                category, first_seen_at, last_seen_at, occurrence_count, resolved_at
            ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
